OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FGreen Party leader Zack Polanski has
OL,8,Fsaid police should not be above
OL,9,Fscrutiny, following controversy over a
OL,10,Fpost he shared about the police
OL,11,Fofficer's response to the Golders
OL,12,FGreen attack.
OL,14,FPolanski retweeted a post which had
OL,15,Faccused the officers of "repeatedly
OL,16,Fand violently kicking a mentally ill
OL,17,Fman in the head" when he was already
OL,18,Fincapacitated from being tasered.
OL,26,@wD@YOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
