FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777971986
OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FHe has faced criticism from within his
OL,8,Fown ranks, as well as from Prime
OL,9,FMinister Keir Starmer who branded him
OL,10,F"disgraceful" and "not fit to lead any
OL,11,Fpolitical party".
OL,13,FPolanski has since apologised for
OL,14,Fsharing the post.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@MO]rD@SOUsD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777971986
OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FSpeaking on Sky News' Sunday Morning
OL,8,FWith Trevor Phillips, Polanski said:
OL,9,F"I think you can both recognise the
OL,10,Fbravery of officers who run towards
OL,11,Fincidents that most of us, including
OL,12,Fmyself, would certainly want to run
OL,13,Faway from, and find the appropriate
OL,14,Fforum to say that no one, especially
OL,15,Fthe police, should be above scrutiny.
OL,17,F"The reason why I've apologised is I
OL,18,Faccept that wasn't the appropriate
OL,19,Fforum."
OL,26,@qD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777971986
OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FHe also hit out at Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fchief Sir Mark Rowley ` who wrote an
OL,9,Fopen letter criticising the politician
OL,10,Fover the repost ` saying the
OL,11,Fcommissioner's move was not "an
OL,12,Fappropriate way to do politics".
OL,14,F"Open letters aren't an appropriate
OL,15,Fway to do politics either in a local
OL,16,Felection," he said of Rowley's letter,
OL,17,F"but I accept all of that, and I'll be
OL,18,Fhaving that conversation with the
OL,19,Fcommissioner".
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@_O]vD@AOUxD@JO]yD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
