OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FCabinet minister Heidi Alexander said
OL,8,Fon Sunday that she could see herself
OL,9,Fkicking the suspect in the attack if
OL,10,Fshe was a police officer.
OL,12,FThe Transport Secretary told Times
OL,13,FRadio: "I thought that if I was in the
OL,14,Fshoes of that police officer then if
OL,15,FI'm honest, given the situation and
OL,16,Fthe fact that he had a backpack on his
OL,17,Fback and they were worried about
OL,18,Fwhether that might go off, I could if
OL,19,FI was a police officer, frankly, I
OL,20,Fcould see myself having taken similar
OL,21,Faction."
OL,26,@uD@HOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
