OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FAlleged attacker Essa Suleiman, 45, is
OL,8,Faccused of trying to kill Shloime
OL,9,FRand, 34, and Norman Shine, 76, during
OL,10,Fa knife rampage through the streets of
OL,11,Fthe north London suburb.
OL,13,FHe has also been charged with the
OL,14,Fattempted murder of a third man, who
OL,15,Fis alleged to have known him, in south
OL,16,FLondon earlier that day.
OL,18,FHe appeared at Westminster
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on Friday morning
OL,20,Fand was remanded in custody.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
