OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FPolanski was also drawn into the
OL,13,Fdebate around chanting "globalise the
OL,14,Fintifada" at demonstrations, and said
OL,15,Fhe discourages the use of the phrase
OL,16,Fbut that he is "not interested" in
OL,17,Fpolicing language.
OL,26,@uD@XOUvD@IO]xD@POUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
