OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777971986
OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FIt comes after the prime minister said
OL,8,Fprotesters have a responsibility to
OL,9,Fcall out chants of the words at Gaza
OL,10,Fmarches.
OL,12,FThe Green Party leader told the BBC's
OL,13,FSunday With Laura Kuenssberg programme
OL,14,Fthat it is not a phrase he would
OL,15,Fpersonally use.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
