PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777971986
OL,3,CPolice should not be above scrutiny,
OL,4,CZack Polanski says over Golders Green
OL,5,Cpost
OL,7,FHe added: "Words matter, but the tens
OL,8,Fof thousands of Palestinians who have
OL,9,Fbeen murdered, the people in Lebanon
OL,10,Fwho have been killed, these people
OL,11,Fmatter too, and I think if people want
OL,12,Fto protest, that it's important we
OL,13,Fdefend their right to protest.
OL,15,F"Yes I do discourage, to give you a
OL,16,Fmore direct answer, the use of the
OL,17,Fphrase but I'm not interested in
OL,18,Ftrying to police people's language."
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@AOUzD@dO]
